{"tid":228602,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真討論）金庸胸部最大女角是誰","createTime":"2017-05-04T04:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:51:38.000Z","uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccddec20a2676f43abc8f67a440e990aaac99a5f","tid":228602,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"Re: [問卦] 金庸胸部最大女角是誰<br />\n<br />\n本大叔根據國中上課研習(偷看)金庸小說多年經驗 分析一下眾多網友的答案<br />\n<br />\n1.黃蓉<br />\n<br />\n她檢了十來個大紅蘋果放入懷中，卻見黃蓉從懷中取出兩隻蘋果，雙手各持一隻，笑吟吟的高高舉起，每隻蘋果上都刺著一枚銀針。李莫愁這才省悟 ，原來她懷中藏著蘋果，先前自己發射暗器，她並不撥打閃避，卻伸手入懷抓住蘋果， 對準銀針的來路，收去了毒針，再誘使自己出掌擊在蘋果之上。by神雕俠侶27 斗智斗力<br />\n<br />\n這段直接宣判黃蓉的胸部size..就是小..能藏這麼多蘋果沒被看出來<br />\n<img src=\"http://juji123.com/img2/role/00/09/93/p00099333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjuji123.com%2Fimg2%2Frole%2F00%2F09%2F93%2Fp00099333.jpg&h=a391a7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.公孫綠萼<br />\n<br />\n膚色白裡泛紅，甚是嬌美，而且秀雅脫俗，自有一般清靈之氣，笑時腰肢嬝娜，楊過在窗外見她全身晶瑩潔白，身材豐腴，容顏俏麗，一看之下，不由得血脈賁張，敗露行藏。by神鵰<br />\n<br />\n因為綠萼的腰肢頗細，所以豐腴的部分顯然不在她腰上。也不可能再腰部以下，所以豐腴要豐腴在什麼地方勒..除了胸還能有什麼地方..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.王語嫣<br />\n<br />\n但見畫中裸女嫣然微笑，眉梢眼角，唇邊頰上，盡是妖媚，比之那玉像的莊嚴寶相，容貌雖似，神情卻是大異。 他似乎聽到自己一顆心撲通、撲通的跳動之聲，斜眼偷看那裸女身子時，只見有一條綠色細線起自左肩，橫至頸下，斜行而至右乳。 他看到畫中裸女椒乳墳起，心中大動，急忙閉眼，過了良久才睜眼再看<br />\n<br />\n後來段譽遇到了王語嫣，王語嫣的相貌居然和無量山石洞中的玉像的相貌全然的一般。<br />\n<img src=\"http://anh.khampha.vn/upload/4-2014/images/2014-10-02/1412245855-luu-diec-phi--9-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fanh.khampha.vn%2Fupload%2F4-2014%2Fimages%2F2014-10-02%2F1412245855-luu-diec-phi--9-.jpg&h=e6922ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-3887095-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-3887095-1-1.html&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=463104c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-3887095-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"46ad30df07237c2af287aa914f7b8330d0e50389","tid":228602,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgtu.5011.net/uploads/content/lishi/miwen/2015-09-09/ebdc19593d84076817099edcb7d77b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgtu.5011.net%2Fuploads%2Fcontent%2Flishi%2Fmiwen%2F2015-09-09%2Febdc19593d84076817099edcb7d77b2c.jpg&h=a3e152ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.23yy.com/upload/2015/11/05/7e375d60-d093-4b2c-a7cc-402ddf07c2ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23yy.com%2Fupload%2F2015%2F11%2F05%2F7e375d60-d093-4b2c-a7cc-402ddf07c2ad.jpg&h=39ce310d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b53f9681f8a0117679ffb8438e9396510c554212","tid":228602,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://imgtu.5011.net/uploads/content/lishi/miwen/2015-09-09/ebdc19593d84076817099edcb7d77b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgtu.5011.net%2Fuploads%2Fcontent%2Flishi%2Fmiwen%2F2015-09-09%2Febdc19593d84076817099edcb7d77b2c.jpg&h=a3e152ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.23yy.com/upload/2015/11/05/7e375d60-d093-4b2c-a7cc-402ddf07c2ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23yy.com%2Fupload%2F2015%2F11%2F05%2F7e375d60-d093-4b2c-a7cc-402ddf07c2ad.jpg&h=39ce310d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}